org.infiniquery.model.view

Class QueryResultsView

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.infiniquery.model.view.QueryResultsView

  • public class QueryResultsView
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of the results of a dynamic query execution. This bean contains both the results list and the display name of the entity type that has been requested. The latter can be used to identify the functions to be used for handling the presentation of the results in UI.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Daniel Doboga
